1 - clone this repo in the user folder
2 - ln -s ~/dotfiles/.zshrc ~/.zshrc
3 - ln -s ~/dotfiles/.dotfiles/neovim.vim ~/.config/nvim/init.vim
4 - ln -s ~/dotfiles/.tmux.conf ~/.tmux.conf


Prerequisites 
- zsh
- ohmyzsh
- asdf
- fzf
- ripgrep
- neovim
- autojump
- exa
- fd
- delta
- bat


shortcuts
TERMINAL: ctrl + space -> autocomplete and runs the written command
TERMINAL: ctrl + e -> just autocomplete the command
TERMINAL: ctrl + r -> search a command in the history
TERMINAL: ctrl + o -> search a folder in the current directory
TERMINAL: ctrl + P -> search and open a file in the current directory

More shortcuts is available inside of alias_commands.zsh
